- Sistem Kelistrikan: For mixing trial bathes of concrete for mix design, Approx 70 ltr capacity, 4 mixing blades, welded steel frame, 2 wheels for easy movement, electromotor 1/3 HP, 220 V-AC, 1 Phase. Dimension (l x w x h) = 20 x 20 x 30 cm. Konfigurasi ini membantu operasional alat berjalan lebih stabil dan mudah dikendalikan.
